A man, with 5 guards in his vicinity, approaches your ship as you land.\
"Hello, my name is Ekrid Malrow, and I represent the company known as the Anti-Raider and Pirate Intelligence Agency, ARPIA for short.  Arpia offers its services everywhere in space.  We are here for the protection of Traders and other non-military people."\
\
This plug-in adds 3 new major storylines to EV Nova, woven in parallel.  Have you ever wanted to play the regular member, not the public figure?  Or the person who stays in the shadows?  In ARPIA2 you get to choose your path.  But beware: one choice can change the future, and the future holds many surprises\'85 Do you have what it takes?\
At first, it is a new system made available once you get to know Arpia (if you succeed in finding it).  It soon becomes a gold mine for new ships and outfits.  Though that is not the only gold mine.  Due to this new application of their properties, the market in Gwaark Bacteria has taken massive proportions, and there is money in it\'85  It has always been everyone's dream to fight off entire fleets by oneself, to become a big-time rich trader, to do covert ops and to know everyone, everywhere.  Well, here's your chance.\
