\i\b \cf0 Installation instructions
\b0 :
\i0 \
For Mac:\
Included in the package is an automatic launcher of ARPIA2 for those who have EV Nova 1.1 for Mac. No installation is then necessary, as long as you do not move files around.\
If you do not have MacNova 1.1 or do not wish to use the automatic launcher, first un-bin/expand all files in the "Plug-Ins" folder.\
Put the all files that are included in the "Plug-Ins" folder into your Plug-ins folder. Please remove any other plug-ins, as compatibility is not at all guaranteed (read further along for details).\
Note for EVN 1.1 Mac users who do not wish to use the automatic launcher: the method for installing plug-ins under EV Nova 1.1 is different. Plug-ins must be put in the following folder:\
~/Library/Application Support/EV Nova/Plug-Ins/ ("~" designates your User folder). The Plug-Ins folder is created when you first launch EVN 1.1.\
For PC:\
