5. Drag-and-drop the resulting .bin files onto the "Convert Plug-ins.exe" program in your Nova folder.\
6. Read the ReadMe to find out how to install the converted plug-in files. If it doesn't say, or there's no readme, place them in the Nova Plug-ins folder.\
